show.description: When betrayal hides behind designer lehengas and royal smiles, one woman dares to expose the truth. Palace Secrets is a high-stakes tale of revenge, secrets, and power struggles set against the backdrop of a "perfect" wedding. Watch in as loyalty is tested and masks come off dramatically. Watch Now.
